[02:36.96]	Upon a just survey, take Titus' part,
[02:39.89]	And so supplant you for ingratitude,
[02:42.89]	Which Rome reputes to be a heinous sin,
[02:46.11]	Yield at entreats; and then let me alone:
[02:49.40]	I'll find a day to massacre them all
[02:52.47]	And raze their faction and their family,
[02:55.76]	The cruel father and his traitorous sons,
[02:59.12]	To whom I sued for my dear son's life,
